"https://donghotuanhung.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GEMAX-52181PR3W-dong-ho-tuan-hung-1.jpg\" style=\"height:400px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n', 1, '1564048273GEMAX-58003R3W-1000x1000-7.jpg', 2263500),
